        {
            "title": "大埔酒樓碗底邊黏「嚼過的肉」 匙羮剩上手食物 網民嘲：頭盤前菜｜Juicy叮",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"大埔酒樓碗底邊黏「嚼過的肉」 匙羮剩上手食物 網民嘲：頭盤前菜\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/c516288c8160086a5694360cd2c0a12c/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022014151258007.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\">大埔酒樓碗底邊黏「嚼過的肉」 匙羮剩上手食物 網民嘲：頭盤前菜</figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>食肆餐具不潔淨衞生，隨時令食客卻步，被列入黑名單不再光顧，情況可大可小。繼<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/local-topics/3426126/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E6%9D%AF%E9%82%8A%E8%AA%87%E5%BC%B5%E9%99%B3%E5%B9%B4%E5%8E%9A%E6%BC%AC-%E6%89%8B%E7%94%B2%E5%88%AE%E5%BE%97%E7%94%A9-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%89%93%E5%86%B7%E9%9C%87Juicy%E5%8F%AE\">屯門商場有冰室杯邊積有手甲刮得甩的陳年厚漬</a>後，大埔有食客早前在一酒樓準備用膳時，嚇然在碗底邊發現黏有一塊懷疑「嚼過的肉」，匙羮更剩有上手食物，感到相當嘔心。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/local-topics/3426126/%E5%B1%AF%E9%96%80%E5%95%86%E5%A0%B4%E5%86%B0%E5%AE%A4%E6%9D%AF%E9%82%8A%E8%AA%87%E5%BC%B5%E9%99%B3%E5%B9%B4%E5%8E%9A%E6%BC%AC-%E6%89%8B%E7%94%B2%E5%88%AE%E5%BE%97%E7%94%A9-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%89%93%E5%86%B7%E9%9C%87Juicy%E5%8F%AE\">屯門商場冰室杯邊誇張陳年厚漬 手甲刮得甩 網民打冷震</a>\n</p><h2>大埔酒樓碗底邊黏嘔心肉碎逐張睇 ＋ 網民嘔心↓↓↓↓</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092467/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"樓主：4800元一圍套餐，這樣的環境一點胃口也沒有，隨便吃兩口。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/7476462290f09cb7c8ee88fc8524d49b/2025-02/1_1_58.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        樓主：4800元一圍套餐，這樣的環境一點胃口也沒有，隨便吃兩口。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092468/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"樓主帖文。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f90184c2ff1067fa13a0afbdd733f44d/2025-02/2_1_63.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        樓主帖文。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092469/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網民：點解你會知舊肉係嚼唔爛？。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/cf105d9e939b79f089354ec5390b2984/2025-02/3_1_113.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民：點解你會知舊肉係嚼唔爛？。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092470/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"樓主拿著碗展示肉碎。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/878e98bf9187210414b1d2c76c70f182/2025-02/4_1_55.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        樓主拿著碗展示肉碎。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092471/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網民：頭盤前菜嚟。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/bb5ac3d1a759da9481270bb9e591799b/2025-02/5_1_31.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民：頭盤前菜嚟。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092472/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網民：邊間鋪？fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/8cf46ab3a93a9e6ff0056c64ffbe52d9/2025-02/6_1_47.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民：邊間鋪？fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<h2>樓主：上次餐廳沙爹牛肉麵吃煙頭</h2>\n<p>塗有紅色指甲的樓主早前在facebook群組「大埔人大埔谷」發帖，大呻「上次某餐廳沙爹牛肉麵裏吃煙頭，今次某酒樓餐前洗餐具，碗底（有）一大塊疑似嚼過的肉，勺子髒兮兮的黏住上一餐的食物。\n\n</p>\n<p>4800元一圍套餐，這樣的環境一點胃口也沒有，隨便吃兩口。外出就餐主打眼不見為淨。#啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊啊，#純吐糟」。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/local-topics/3418725/%E5%A4%A7%E5%9F%94%E8%8C%B6%E8%A8%98%E5%A5%87%E8%91%A9%E5%B8%B8%E9%A4%90-%E6%B8%85%E6%B0%B4%E6%B9%AF%E5%BA%95%E5%8D%B3%E9%A3%9F%E9%BA%B5-%E9%A3%9F%E5%AE%A2%E7%8B%82%E8%97%90%E5%BE%97%E9%99%A3%E5%91%B3Juicy%E5%8F%AE\" target=\"_blank\">大埔茶記奇葩常餐 清水湯底即食麵 食客狂藐：得陣Ｘ味</a>\n</p><h2>大埔酒樓碗底邊黏嘔心肉碎逐張睇 ＋ 網民嘔心↓↓↓↓</h2>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092475/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"碗底邊的疑似嚼過的肉。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/b7287af66941d310ac8e9404aace814b/2025-02/7N_6.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        碗底邊的疑似嚼過的肉。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092476/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"樓主：純吐槽，不開名。畢竟沒有過分到食物裏面出現異物。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/e8474ebbc2a756df6f1470373eeb3998/2025-02/8_0_124.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        樓主：純吐槽，不開名。畢竟沒有過分到食物裏面出現異物。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092477/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"樓主寫上長文大呻。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/53abc0880aae87c0b4eab2d2df23c350/2025-02/9_1_38.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        樓主寫上長文大呻。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092478/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網民：無計喇，個巿咁好，請得啲乜人做洗碗。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/40a2bb90cd3b9d5a3742919bd8d1a71d/2025-02/10_0_118.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民：無計喇，個巿咁好，請得啲乜人做洗碗。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092479/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網民：未開席已經上菜，咁抵！fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/d95eef39b2d516ddc3f8d18cd0af9fc8/2025-02/11_1_24.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民：未開席已經上菜，咁抵！fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\" data-watermark-position=\"\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092480/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"網民：呢個餐前小吃應該收咗你錢。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/71253b139502318341375d58c1adee2e/2025-02/12_0_105.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        網民：呢個餐前小吃應該收咗你錢。fb「大埔人大埔谷」截圖\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\" data-quickedit-field-id=\"media/4092499/thumbnail/zh-hant/media_library\"> <img alt=\"大埔酒樓碗底邊黏嘔心肉碎 匙羮剩上手食物 網民嘲：頭盤前菜  ​\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f40b01f8c5f819ba38d902c0c58a443b/2025-02/21_48.png\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        大埔酒樓碗底邊黏嘔心肉碎 匙羮剩上手食物 網民嘲：頭盤前菜  ​\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n<h2>網民：頭盤前菜嚟</h2>\n<p>回應的網民苦中作樂，嘲笑碗底的這一塊「疑似嚼過的肉」是「頭盤前菜嚟」、「呢個餐前小吃應該收咗你錢」、「未開席已經上菜，咁抵！」；有人則安慰樓主，稱「無計喇，個巿咁好，請得啲乜人做洗碗」。\n\n</p>\n<p>另有人斟酌樓主的留言，查問「點解你會知舊肉係嚼唔爛？」，獲樓主幽默地回覆「可能我試了一下」。有網民關心涉事食肆的大寶號，詢問「邊間鋪」，樓主則指「純吐糟，不開名。畢竟沒有過分到食物裏面出現異物」。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關閱讀：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/local-topics/3406581/%E9%95%B7%E6%B2%99%E7%81%A3%E9%85%92%E6%A8%93%E9%BB%9E%E5%BF%83%E9%A9%9A%E8%A6%8B%E8%80%81%E9%BC%A0%E5%B1%8E-%E4%BA%8B%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%80%E5%BE%8C%E5%92%81%E8%99%95%E7%90%86%E9%A3%9F%E6%85%BE%E7%9B%A1%E5%A4%B1Juicy%E5%8F%AE\" target=\"_blank\">長沙灣酒樓點心驚見「老鼠屎」 事主最後咁處理：食慾盡失！</a>\n</p>\n<p> \n\n\n\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner2\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,2,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner2-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n</div>",
