            "title": "中方包機抵達泰國  接回從緬甸電詐園區遣返的中國籍人員",
            "description": "<div class=\"video paragraphs medium\">\n<p> <figure class=\"margin-top-1\">\n<img alt=\"\" class=\"size-full w-100\" src=\"https://image.stheadline.com/f/680p0/0x0/100/none/43b08a9fa1f21bcd358450e9c86782a6/stheadline/inewsmedia/20250220/_2025022014052024158.jpg\"/>\n<figcaption class=\"caption-text\"></figcaption>\n</figure>\n</p>\n<div class=\"in-article-banner\">\n<div class=\"mx-auto web\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,1\" id=\"inarticlebanner1\"></div>\n<div class=\"mx-auto mweb\" data-slot=\"inarticlebanner,1,2\" id=\"inarticlebanner1-MWeb\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>央視新聞消息，當地時間20日上午，一架中方包機降落在泰緬邊境泰國一側的湄索機場，接回從緬甸詐騙園區被遣返的中國籍人員。首批被遣返人員登機後，中方第一架包機已飛離機場。\n\n</p>\n<p>除首架包機外，後續還將有多架包機陸續抵達湄索機場，繼續將被遣返人員接回國內。\n\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"泰國軍車到緬甸邊境接收詐騙園區遺返人員。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" src=\"https://image.hkhl.hk/f/1024p0/0x0/100/none/f8ba42bd136ed74484ee79a49ea86544/2025-02/0220025.jpg\" typeof=\"foaf:Image\" width=\"100%\"/>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"media-library-item__attributes\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__name\">\n        泰國軍車到緬甸邊境接收詐騙園區遺返人員。\n      </div>\n</div>\n</article>\n</p>\n<p>當天稍早前，在泰國緬甸邊境，泰國軍方人員與警方開始從緬甸方面接收中國公民，這些中國公民是緬甸方面從詐騙園區遣送出來的相關人員。據悉，所有中國公民將被送往泰國一側的湄索機場，乘坐中方包機航班，於當天返回中國。\n\n</p>\n<p>相關新聞：<a href=\"https://www.stheadline.com/realtime-world/3430287/%E7%B7%AC%E7%94%B8%E8%A9%90%E9%A8%99%E5%9C%92%E5%8D%80%E7%B8%BD%E7%90%86%E4%BD%A9%E9%80%9A%E5%9D%A6%E6%8C%877000%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%B2%E6%95%91-%E5%BE%85%E8%BD%89%E7%A7%BB%E8%87%B3%E6%B3%B0%E5%9C%8B\">緬甸詐騙園區｜總理佩通坦指7000人獲救 待轉移至泰國</a>\n<article class=\"align-center\">\n<div class=\"media-library-item__preview js-media-library-item-preview\">\n<div class=\"field field--name-thumbnail field--type-image field--label-hidden field__item\"> <img alt=\"中國的包機到達泰國機場。\" class=\"image-style-medium\" sr